data.description: This cute and cozy 2 bed 1 bath home offers a view of Turtleback Mountain, mature trees such as pecan, pomegranate, willow and non-fruiting mulberry. Inside features include custom kitchen cabinets, stainless steel appliances, mud room with room for storage. Open living room with gas log fireplace. There is a wall furnace that heats both bedrooms and two evaporative coolers to stay cool in the summer. Half of the property is fenced leaving additional room for more parking or even a garage. This property has a lot of potential and is conveniently located to restaurants and commercial businesses that beautiful TorC has to offer!
